52, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smithcut a relaxed figureas she counted down the days to the start of the Paris Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a relaxed figureas\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the hard work has been done, having worked tirelessly with her trusted coachRocco Meiringahead of her second Games.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the hard work\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 516}, {\"ngram\": \"her trusted coachRocco Meiringahead\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 597}, {\"ngram\": \"her second Games\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section In Tokyo three years ago she still managed to win silver in the women's 100m breaststroke (her time of 1:04.82 came in the semi-finals) and gold in the 200m despite an interrupted schedule given the complications related to the Covid-19 pandemic as well as load shedding.\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999976152972195, \"rank\": 2.384726418376591e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 100m breaststroke\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"1:04.82\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"an interrupted schedule\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"the complications\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the Covid-19\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"load\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On that occasion, her debut Olympics, she said she was using the 100m as a springboard for her main event, the 200m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that occasion\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"a springboard\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"her main event\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a tried and tested strategy, also producing a silver-gold at the 2022 Commonwealth Games, although double gold at those 2018 Games.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tried and tested strategy\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver-gold\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"those 2018 Games\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old is in Paris with a target on her back.\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.828174110375918e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"her back\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's second fastest in the world over 100m at these Games and the quickest over 200m.\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"100m\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"the quickest over 200m.\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's always marrying rankings with a prediction, but there is a steely inner-belief behind that smile that has the cameras flashing.\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rankings\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"a prediction\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"a steely inner-belief\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"that smile\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"the cameras\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith is a natural competitor, and a born racer.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural competitor\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1561}, {\"ngram\": \"a born racer\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pretty much as Chad le Clos is, and showed in his prime.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chad le Clos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chad_le_Clos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his prime\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One race at a time and get into the final.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One race\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once in the final it's game on.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"game\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Tang Qianting heads the 2024 rankings with a best of 1:04.39, with Smith third after a 1:05.41 in April.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1714, \"end\": 1719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9490484116562116, \"rank\": 0.05368679563923408, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tang Qianting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1:04.39\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"a 1:05.41\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The meat in the sandwich is Russian Evgeniia Chukinova who has withdrawn from Paris, opening the way for the South African to be the Chinese swimmer's biggest threat.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1855, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9818980411410214, \"rank\": 0.01843197255805531, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.828174110375918e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9924403027106089, \"rank\": 0.007466294402182655, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The meat\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1835}, {\"ngram\": \"the sandwich\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the South African\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, is it the other way round?\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without making any predictions,all the smart money is on Smith winning two medals, which would place her with four alongside Le Clos in terms of Team SA's Olympic roll of honour.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.218042686579111e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any predictions\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"all the smart money\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"two medals\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"honour\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith has been her normal jovial self, although one could detect just the slightest hint of \\\"let us just get started\\\" this week, which is a good thing.\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2212}, {\"ngram\": \"her normal jovial self\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"just the slightest hint\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"a good thing\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's in the DNA of every top sports person.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the DNA\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"every top sports person\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, coach Meiring is always one to stand in the background and deflect attention, but he has been walking around the village with the slightest trace of a smile all week.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coach Meiring\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"the slightest trace\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost as it saying,\\\"Suid Afrika, hulle weet nie wat ons weet nie\\\".\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7578990254390642e-15, \"text\": \"Afrika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hulle weet nie wat ons weet nie\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Smith it's following something that has worked so well before.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's on the brink of becoming Team SA's most garlanded Olympian, and only from two such Games.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.218042686579111e-19, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 2772, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999988358468, \"rank\": 1.1641581050780205e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the brink\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"two such Games\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a case of (trying to) perfect the small things a swimming is very technical, It's those small margins that count, I do not think physically we can do much more.\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"the small things\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"a swimming\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"those small margins\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The one difference is that you are growing as a person and you are changing.\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one difference\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am getting older, so that's a massive difference compared to Tokyo, but otherwise it's just the same, trying to get it right every time.\\\"\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999976152972195, \"rank\": 2.384726418376591e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive difference\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, the Team SA tone has been set by the swimmers.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team SA tone\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimmers\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whenever swimming has gone without a medal, as in 1992 and 2008, the return was two medals overall and one.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3303}, {\"ngram\": \"the return\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore the expectations are there for Smith to deliver in Paris.\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.828174110375918e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does not faze her.\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a daily thing that you have to tell yourself that you are not swimming for others' expectations.\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a daily thing\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"others' expectations\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think sometimes my own expectations are higher than those others!, For me, I trust in God and know that His plan will ultimately work out.\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own expectations\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"those others\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"His plan\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can only prepare as well as I can, and whatever happens on that day happens.\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3753}, {\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always say that in Tokyo, maybe if we raced the day after, someone else could have been Olympic champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999976152972195, \"rank\": 2.384726418376591e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can see how humble she remains, fame and deserved fortune not going to her head.\", \"from\": 3893, \"to\": 3977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fame\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"deserved fortune\", \"from\": 3938, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"her head\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, the time schedule is different to Tokyo, with the finals being raced in the evening whereas they were in the mornings at the 2020 Game, but the format is the same.\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3981, \"end\": 3986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.828174110375918e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4022, \"end\": 4027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999976152972195, \"rank\": 2.384726418376591e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time schedule\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 4005}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"the evening\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4071}, {\"ngram\": \"the mornings\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4105}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Game\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4122}, {\"ngram\": \"the format\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 100 is always first and it's always nice to have as a pre-race for the 200 metres.\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pre\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4215}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4220}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200 metres\", \"from\": 4225, \"to\": 4239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I start enjoying it too much and then get nervous, thinking 'how am I going survive in the 200', but it is always good to just see where I am and have that easy speed in the beginning.\", \"from\": 4241, \"to\": 4435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that easy speed\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to stay calm in this.\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about how we react to situations and how positive we are in those situations that count.\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"situations\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4504}, {\"ngram\": \"those situations\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am just saying positive.\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it's going to go well, and I have prepared well.'\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That last statement is a gold nugget of intent.\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That last statement\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4668}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold nugget\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4685}, {\"ngram\": \"intent\", \"from\": 4689, \"to\": 4695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, be prepared to see the name Smith step onto the podium in Paris, perhaps twice.\", \"from\": 4698, \"to\": 4781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4760, \"end\": 4765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.828174110375918e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4735}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now married to Joel, she is loving life and admits she is still \\\"getting used to seeing a very short surnam